text: Nem danifuwotsnat ferisawino etfwotso, be'ewosha etaat geenzidek'at Ik'o it k'onirwats weebdek'at t'oow máátsuwots detstso ishbaziruwotso indowe itsha! manshe itatse ikibog angsho bodetuwe.]23:14 Matiyos mas'fotsere tatse awdl taawan aaliye ik ik shin kishon guut'ets mas'fotse aaliye, Mar. 12:40 nat Luk'. 20:47 atse fa'ee.
